<Link id="l00448" /><CodeLine lineNumber="448"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// There&#39;s a &quot;bug&quot; in the DWARFv3 standard with respect to the target address</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l00453" /><CodeLine lineNumber="453"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// other tools (libdwarf) and extract this from the container (ObjectFile</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l00454" /><CodeLine lineNumber="454"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// provides this information). This problem is fixed in DWARFv4</span></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01921" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1921"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// First calculate the address of the symbol or section as it appears</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01922" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1922"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// in the object file</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01923" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1923"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (Sym != Obj.<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/symbolicfile/#a7bc0f444aecc9b7aaef7facdb3d2bddb">symbol&#95;end</a>()) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01924" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1924"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordType">bool</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> New;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01925" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1925"><span class="doxyHighlight">    std::tie(CacheIt, New) = Cache.insert(&#123;&#42;Sym, &#123;0, 0&#125;&#125;);</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01926" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1926"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (!New)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01927" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1927"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">return</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> CacheIt-&gt;second;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01928" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1928"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01929" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1929"><span class="doxyHighlight">    <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/expected">Expected&lt;uint64&#95;t&gt;</a> SymAddrOrErr = Sym-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/symbolref/#ac22d03239bd28b53a229486b43a9d3b8">getAddress</a>();</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01930" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1930"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (!SymAddrOrErr)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01931" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1931"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">return</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a7f159cd1ce91fea2e7ed0b1de3b381b9">createError</a>(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;failed to compute symbol address: &quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01932" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1932"><span class="doxyHighlight">                         SymAddrOrErr.<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/expected/#a94789df4ebd03dc008e8adebaa66ac1f">takeError</a>());</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01933" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1933"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01934" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1934"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// Also remember what section this symbol is in for later</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01935" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1935"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">auto</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> SectOrErr = Sym-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/symbolref/#af8b31890b3cf3677a9c279325661e3af">getSection</a>();</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01936" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1936"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (!SectOrErr)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01937" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1937"><span class="doxyHighlight">      </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">return</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a7f159cd1ce91fea2e7ed0b1de3b381b9">createError</a>(</span><span class="doxyHighlightStringLiteral">&quot;failed to get symbol section: &quot;</span><span class="doxyHighlight">,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01938" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1938"><span class="doxyHighlight">                         SectOrErr.takeError());</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01939" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1939"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01940" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1940"><span class="doxyHighlight">    RSec = &#42;SectOrErr;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01941" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1941"><span class="doxyHighlight">    Ret.Address = &#42;SymAddrOrErr;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01942" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1942"><span class="doxyHighlight">  &#125; </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">else</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (</span><span class="doxyHighlightKeyword">auto</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> &#42;MObj = <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a22eeee01734061ac1b31ccd994c49eef">dyn&#95;cast&lt;MachOObjectFile&gt;</a>(&amp;Obj)) &#123;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01943" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1943"><span class="doxyHighlight">    RSec = MObj-&gt;getRelocationSection(<a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/reloc">Reloc</a>.getRawDataRefImpl());</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01944" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1944"><span class="doxyHighlight">    Ret.Address = RSec-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/sectionref/#a9a664da9a987e7bb5023e33705509df4">getAddress</a>();</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01945" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1945"><span class="doxyHighlight">  &#125;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01946" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1946"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01947" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1947"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (RSec != Obj.<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/objectfile/#a3e48ce01c39d5e5e36eced4e3d3f6f23">section&#95;end</a>())</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01948" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1948"><span class="doxyHighlight">    Ret.SectionIndex = RSec-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/sectionref/#a1683493667fa7e44083fe1258a1dcb10">getIndex</a>();</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01949" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1949"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01950" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1950"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// If we are given load addresses for the sections, we need to adjust:</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01951" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1951"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// SymAddr = (Address of Symbol Or Section in File) -</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01952" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1952"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//           (Address of Section in File) +</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01953" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1953"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">//           (Load Address of Section)</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01954" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1954"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// RSec is now either the section being targeted or the section</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01955" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1955"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// containing the symbol being targeted. In either case,</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01956" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1956"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightComment">// we need to perform the same computation.</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01957" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1957"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (L &amp;&amp; RSec != Obj.<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/objectfile/#a3e48ce01c39d5e5e36eced4e3d3f6f23">section&#95;end</a>())</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01958" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1958"><span class="doxyHighlight">    </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (uint64&#95;t SectionLoadAddress = L-&gt;getSectionLoadAddress(&#42;RSec))</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01959" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1959"><span class="doxyHighlight">      Ret.Address += SectionLoadAddress - RSec-&gt;<a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/object/sectionref/#a9a664da9a987e7bb5023e33705509df4">getAddress</a>();</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01960" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1960"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01961" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1961"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">if</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> (CacheIt != Cache.end())</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01962" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1962"><span class="doxyHighlight">    CacheIt-&gt;second = Ret;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01963" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1963"></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01964" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1964"><span class="doxyHighlight">  </span><span class="doxyHighlightKeywordFlow">return</span><span class="doxyHighlight"> Ret;</span></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01965" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1965"><span class="doxyHighlight">&#125;</span></CodeLine>
